item.title: My 2018 in review
item.description: I figured enough has taken place this year, enough changes have taken place, and I’ve worked on enough projects that a post recapping things might be worthwhile. To start, here’s a playlist of my favorite songs of the year that you can listen to while reading this post. So what did I do with this year? It seems, looking back, I wrote a ton of code.
